newsitem.title: DUBAI: Omani stocks mixed, industrials lead trade.
newsitem.headline: Omani stocks mixed, industrials lead trade.

text.p: Shares on Oman's stock exchange ended the week to Wednesday mixed with industrials dominating trade, the Muscat Securities Market said in a report.
The index lost 1.45 points to 185.72 in the week.
Of the total 54 companies traded in the week, shares of 19 rose, 23 fell and 12 were unchanged, the report said.

Industrials accounted for 37 percent of total trading value of 2.340 million rials ($6.1 million) from last week's 3.328 million rials. The report said 1.183 million shares changed hands during the week.
